    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005840/extras/1585b7a6248578cc1919855300ed1328.poster.avif?t=1765612067\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005840/extras/1585b7a6248578cc1919855300ed1328.webm?t=1765612067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005840/extras/1585b7a6248578cc1919855300ed1328.mp4?t=1765612067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>在 Everglyph Trials 中考验你的智慧和策略，这款轻度 rogue 牌组构筑游戏具有不断变化的选择和挑战。</strong><br>从种类繁多的卡牌中构筑你的牌组，每张卡牌都有独一无二的组合效果。释放强力组合技，并根据情况调整你的策略，击败强大的楼层头目。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005840/extras/bf9ee1180170e9e5c6826b4d7802784a.poster.avif?t=1765612067\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005840/extras/bf9ee1180170e9e5c6826b4d7802784a.webm?t=1765612067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005840/extras/bf9ee1180170e9e5c6826b4d7802784a.mp4?t=1765612067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005840/extras/steam_divider.PNG?t=1765612067\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>充满策略性的牌组构筑：</strong>在你的冒险旅程中做出关键的卡牌选择，打造一套能够克服艰难遭遇的牌组。尝试各种组合技，并随着战场形势的变化调整你的策略。<br></li><li><strong>双卡效果：</strong>每张卡牌都提供两种强力的选项：出牌效果和揭示效果。分析敌人及其意图，执行制胜策略。你会在本回合冒险打出高额伤害，还是为下回合的完美终结进行铺垫？</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005840/extras/cc56bfcf6c7073f78274430367b245a1.poster.avif?t=1765612067\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005840/extras/cc56bfcf6c7073f78274430367b245a1.webm?t=1765612067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005840/extras/cc56bfcf6c7073f78274430367b245a1.mp4?t=1765612067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>协同和增益：</strong>使用同一元素派系的卡牌可以解锁额外效果，例如多重施法和叠加增益。通过深思熟虑的卡牌操作释放每位英雄的潜力。<br></li><li><strong>不断变化的深度：</strong>每次冒险都独一无二。探索随机生成的楼层，遭遇拥有致命技能的各种敌人，并发现可以改变命运的强大符文。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005840/extras/7a0a4896741cf1b9a177a9d26db32a55.poster.avif?t=1765612067\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005840/extras/7a0a4896741cf1b9a177a9d26db32a55.webm?t=1765612067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005840/extras/7a0a4896741cf1b9a177a9d26db32a55.mp4?t=1765612067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>充满魔法和美景的世界：</strong>沉浸于惊艳的手绘奇幻世界，探索令人屏息的景色，与奇幻生物战斗，并揭开其中的秘密。<br></li><li><strong>轻度 rogue 挑战在等着你：</strong>磨练技巧，每次冒险都为你提供学习的机会，解锁永久升级，铸就通往胜利的道路。<br></li><li><strong>硬核模式：</strong>可选择通过更深入的试炼或增加限制来提高难度，以获得更丰厚的奖励。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005840/extras/5e981604881864f3b557e3ca450ff150.poster.avif?t=1765612067\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005840/extras/5e981604881864f3b557e3ca450ff150.webm?t=1765612067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005840/extras/5e981604881864f3b557e3ca450ff150.mp4?t=1765612067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
